Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.55,0:00:18.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来已经没有什么需要我再教了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.30,0:00:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漫长的旅途 让你辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.36,0:00:25.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上就到城镇了 蜜尔佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.01,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}想要见你 却觅不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:33.27,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}思念越发强烈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:37.39,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}无法传达到这份祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:43.98,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}一定是因为	迷失了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:51.70,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}无论何时  只有被映在这眼瞳里的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.16,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}是唯一的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.33,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}一直如此坚信着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.50,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}世界并非唯一
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:06.26,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}还有所谓如果的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:10.26,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}因为存在着无限可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:15.89,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}正迷失着方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:19.65,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}想要见你 却觅不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.65,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}不论你现在身处何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:24.86,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}必定能找到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:30.53,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}不慎闯入了瞳中的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.20,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:36.45,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被黑暗之手遮蔽了去路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:40.58,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}即使被怯弱的心所迷惑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:42.38,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}也不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:46.96,chop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}继续寻找着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.01,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.06,0:00:33.27,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}思いつのるほど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.31,0:00:37.39,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}この祈りが届かないのは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.44,0:00:43.98,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}何かをきっと 見失ってるから
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:51.70,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}いつだって この瞳に 映されたものだけが
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.16,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}唯一の真実だと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:58.33,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}信じていたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.21,0:01:02.50,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}世界は一つじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.05,0:01:06.26,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}もしもという世界
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:10.26,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}無限にあるとして
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.64,0:01:15.89,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}いま途方に暮れている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.60,0:01:19.65,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}会いたい 会えない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.65,0:01:21.65,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}いま何処にいるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.73,0:01:24.86,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}必ず見つけ出すから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.90,0:01:30.53,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}迷い込んだのは瞳の中にある
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:32.20,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}迷宫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:36.45,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}例え暗闇がゆく手を遮り
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.50,0:01:40.58,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}弱気な心惑わせても
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.67,0:01:42.38,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}諦めないで
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.54,0:01:46.96,jpop,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}探しつづけるから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.19,0:02:07.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs26\fad(1200,1200)\be1\bord2\4a&Hc1&\3a&Hc1&\shad3\pos(505,372)}蜜尔佳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.39,0:02:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接着 让我们去看一看下一本书吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:19.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来在这个世界里 好像发生过一点不幸的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰丝加勒丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:29.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的 戴上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.58,0:02:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱 兰丝加勒丝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰丝加勒丝 你去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初美会在这种小岛上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是小啊 是无人岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.01,0:03:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那来这里不是毫无意义吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:12.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 我先去侦察一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.52,0:03:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.19,0:03:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就剩我们两人了呢 叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.65,0:03:24.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别发出那种怪声 恶心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快累趴下了 不减肥不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.17,0:03:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.17,0:03:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊啊 你最好稍微减减肥 跟我一起去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:09.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好重啊 好重 真的好重
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.56,0:04:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好重啊 果然是重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:18.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只鹦鹉全身的皮下脂肪高达100%
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.98,0:04:22.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不想变成大胖子的话最好停手哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.66,0:04:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 快停手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:39.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰丝加勒丝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:44.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.38,0:04:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只虎是你的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:52.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 我是莉莉丝 这位是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:58.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,东叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:01.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 你们要打蜜尔佳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.69,0:05:03.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不会做那种事的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.91,0:05:05.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们要欺负蜜尔佳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会欺负你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳住在这个岛上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住在岛上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:13.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟谁一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.16,0:05:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞伦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.44,0:05:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞伦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塞伦是蜜尔佳的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 像是在哪里听到过的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 莉莉丝也是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.28,0:05:27.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想成为你的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么想成为呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说做朋友什么的 只会吃亏所以让人讨厌的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.85,0:05:37.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁这样说的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.18,0:05:41.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我忘了 是婆婆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个婆婆也是这个岛上的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:48.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 以前在这个岛上 现在不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 叶月是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.06,0:05:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.84,0:05:54.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.66,0:05:55.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.41,0:06:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.87,0:06:10.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.50,0:06:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.05,0:06:33.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么 刚才的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的是“啪哩啪哩”
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啪哩啪哩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:43.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 “啪哩啪哩”是会稍微有点痛的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:47.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 塞伦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.46,0:06:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳大人 您没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.52,0:06:52.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳今天也是没事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:54.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.41,0:06:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这几位是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们想和蜜尔佳成为朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.01,0:07:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以和他们成为朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.88,0:07:15.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 难得各位来拜访这个小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就让我作向导带领各位去行宫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:21.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:31.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 叶月有恋人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:32.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:36.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要长大后就会有恋人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不是这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.80,0:07:47.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓的恋人就是指男人 塞伦是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.15,0:07:53.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳从没见过男人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月见过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:56.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 见过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.12,0:08:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说男人都是很美妙的 是那样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.22,0:08:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月是男人还是女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:08.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:11.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 是女人 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人的奶子不会鼓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.59,0:08:17.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说叶月不是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样说很容易懂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.16,0:08:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶子是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是乳房 关西腔里叫奶子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:29.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳胸部没有鼓起来 蜜尔佳是男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.45,0:08:31.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 不是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.28,0:08:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等蜜尔佳长到这么大时 就会变成“波波”的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时男人就会一个接一个追着你跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:41.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚对像什么的可以随你挑选
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.32,0:08:43.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:09:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好喝 真是好茶叶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道真的不记得我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.55,0:09:13.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那顶帽子 还是让人感到不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.38,0:09:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:33.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰丝加勒丝 重新向叶月打声招呼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是那样 那个孩子也真是古怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:50.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是厉害 你是能够明白的呢 蜜尔佳大人的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:51.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.89,0:09:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为蜜尔佳大人一直没有长大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有长大
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.68,0:10:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳大人从很多年以前开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.51,0:10:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那个样子没有改变了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我之前负责教育蜜尔佳大人的人非常严格
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:09.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎每天都会很严厉地责罚蜜尔佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:12.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那样不知持续了多少年
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为蜜尔佳大人一直保持着小孩子的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.92,0:10:17.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人后来去哪里了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.99,0:10:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从一个年老的婆婆那里听到过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:25.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,某一天 一件惨不忍睹的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个可怕的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:33.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事蜜尔佳知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.46,0:10:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像是不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:42.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.67,0:10:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像吃点心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果烤饼也可以的话 我可以做给你吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗 蜜尔佳好想吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.94,0:10:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么带我去厨房
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.05,0:10:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:56.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.29,0:10:58.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好闻的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.43,0:11:00.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.57,0:11:07.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.49,0:11:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月 你当我家里的厨师吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:17.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真正好吃的烤饼并不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.01,0:11:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经收到过全宇宙第一好吃的烤饼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了 那个人就是叶月的恋人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.87,0:11:28.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:33.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为叶月说话时目光非常的温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.68,0:11:35.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以蜜尔佳就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.97,0:11:50.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天来的真是一些不可思议的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:52.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰丝加勒丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.20,0:12:01.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:16.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.48,0:12:17.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 莉莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.12,0:12:19.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.19,0:12:21.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结婚是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:24.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳大人 从哪里听到那种…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:26.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边那个古怪的鸟先生说的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.91,0:12:28.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是古怪的鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:29.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.86,0:12:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 就是跟男人卿卿我我 然后一直在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.79,0:12:40.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对啊 就是这样 到了晚上 慢慢地 慢慢地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.80,0:12:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等蜜尔佳长大后 一定会有一个美好的婚姻的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.38,0:12:49.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳能长大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 一定能的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.89,0:13:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之 得想办法先解决那个莫名其妙的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.75,0:13:09.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 蜜尔佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.32,0:13:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在睡觉之前要先洗澡哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.26,0:13:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么大家一起去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.26,0:13:20.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 好啊 一起去吧一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.20,0:13:23.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么 干什么 这种处置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.77,0:13:25.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底对我做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.41,0:13:27.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样呢 叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得这么一次 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了 稍后我一个人去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.92,0:13:35.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不用这么害羞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.03,0:13:43.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉丝会去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.66,0:13:48.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是说要在浴池里 帮我教蜜尔佳大人从1数到100吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊 一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.67,0:13:50.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.13,0:13:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 去洗澡的话要脱掉那个帽子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是 要脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.41,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真是让人期待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.64,0:14:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:30.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不要紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.67,0:14:37.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.08,0:14:39.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,“啪哩啪哩”的原因我已经明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.93,0:14:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 蜜尔佳 去洗澡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.10,0:14:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.80,0:14:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.02,0:15:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.13,0:15:07.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取不出来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,莉莉丝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.41,0:15:14.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳已经脱完了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 我的衣服脱起来比较费劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这种时候却…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你是怎么到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.97,0:15:30.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么说都是靠毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.26,0:15:33.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个倒是有件好事情想要告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.95,0:15:34.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.19,0:15:37.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正你是想去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接在这里把礼服脱掉不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:51.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 这样触碰人家的背会让人家有感觉的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:09.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管是莉莉丝还是叶月还是塞伦胸部都好大
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.01,0:16:12.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有蜜尔佳胸部平平的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无须担心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.86,0:16:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女人不只是胸部而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.17,0:16:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳今晚可以跟叶月一起睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.57,0:16:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.74,0:16:49.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.65,0:16:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好啊 叶月的恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:53.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个人可以从叶月这里得到很多的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.64,0:17:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却没有人给蜜尔佳很多的关心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.85,0:17:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原谅我 婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.30,0:17:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天蜜尔佳违反了嘱咐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.94,0:17:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天蜜尔佳说了谎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.05,0:17:39.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天蜜尔佳顶了嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.79,0:17:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天蜜尔佳在心里面说了“婆婆去死”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.52,0:17:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.64,0:17:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:13.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9436
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.74,0:18:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9545
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9654
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:19.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9763
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9872
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.38,0:18:23.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9981
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.40,0:18:25.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 完成的非常好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.25,0:18:29.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由于没有一个错误 可以给一些奖励呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:30.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奖励
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 想要什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:44.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳想要一个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:45.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.49,0:18:46.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一个恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:48.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恋人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.56,0:18:49.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.48,0:18:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话蜜尔佳就可以得到很多的关心 变得很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:55.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能的 你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.73,0:19:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为使用了魔力而让成长停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.62,0:19:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是随便说说罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:16.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:22.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月是从哪里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.14,0:19:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很远 很远的国家来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.15,0:19:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪个国家里有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.81,0:19:30.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么东西都有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.24,0:19:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是全都非常无趣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:34.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里大概有多少人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:37.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多得让人讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人跟女人都有吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:40.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.13,0:19:44.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶月为何没跟恋人在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.09,0:19:48.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不在了 所以我正在找他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.24,0:19:52.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳也想去找找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.21,0:19:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳的恋人在哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.28,0:19:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在这个海的对面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.89,0:20:01.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海的对面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.51,0:20:09.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又开始了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.36,0:20:25.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.78,0:20:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.45,0:20:35.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的“啪哩啪哩”比以往都要长 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.10,0:20:43.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小黑鬼 停手 快停手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.78,0:20:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:53.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳要去海的对面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:04.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 蜜尔佳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜜尔佳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:41.45,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠の祈りをささげて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:48.17,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}大事なもの諦めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.09,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}どんなに遠くても
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.09,0:22:02.47,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}きっと捕まえてみせる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.51,0:22:10.23,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}君と僕との それが約束
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.27,0:22:17.28,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}思いでも 抱きしめないでいても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.36,0:22:24.70,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}気持ちは 一つも届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:33.09,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}永遠お祈りをささげて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.09,0:22:39.84,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}大事なもの諦めたりしない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:48.73,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}君と僕の間にひかる夜明けをみつけて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.14,0:22:57.86,jped,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,500)}もらすぐ始まる明日を迎えにゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:41.45,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}献上永远的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.66,0:21:48.17,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}切莫放弃珍贵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.09,ched,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(220,220)}无论多么遥远
